Welcome to my Titanium MVC example.  This repository is the source companion to my recent post on Titanium MVC: http://bradbroulik.blogspot.com/2011/03/titanium-mvc-pattern.html


1) Import this project into your Titanium workspace.
2) Launch the project from your iPhone emulator to run the example.
3) The controller and view files are in /Resources/src/MVC/ui/*.
